飓风艾琳一共造成18人死亡（其中15人属间接导致），经济损失8亿美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|800000000|1999}}}}美元）。大部分破坏和人员丧生都是因风暴引发的倾盆大雨导致。

=== 古巴 ===
艾琳途经古巴期间产生了暴雨，局部降雨量高达905毫米<ref>{{cite web |author=Alejandro Bezanilla |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224082645/http://www.met.inf.cu/sometcuba/boletin/v06_n01/english/season4.htm |date=2000-01 |title=Cyclone Season of 1999 on the North Atlantic Ocean |work=SOMETCUBA Bulletin |publisher=Cuban Meteorological Society |url=http://www.met.inf.cu/sometcuba/boletin/v06_n01/english/season4.htm |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-07-27 |archivedate=2013-12-24 }}</ref>。[[马坦萨斯省|马坦萨斯省]]的[[吉隆滩|吉隆滩]]（{{lang|es|Playa Girón}}）记录下303毫米降水，[[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]也记录下了122毫米<ref name="cubreport">{{cite web | author = Mary Miranda | year = 1999 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224101111/http://www.cubafreepress.org/art2/cubap991015f.html | title = Four Dead or Missing; Thousands Evacuated as a Result of Irene | publisher = Cuba Free Press | accessdate = 2014-07-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cubafreepress.org/art2/cubap991015f.html | archivedate = 2013-12-24 }}</ref>，还有其他多个地点记录下超过178毫米降雨量。此外，哈瓦那记录下的最强阵风时速为126公里<ref name="tcr" />。

风暴引发的洪灾破坏了超过1900[[平方公里|平方公里]][[甘蔗|甘蔗]]种植园和158平方公里香蕉种植园<ref name="cubcrop">{{cite web | author = CubaNet News | year = 1999 | title = Cuba revela nuevas cifras de daños causados por huracán Irene | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320175205/http://www.cubanet.org/CNews/y99/oct99/25o12.htm | accessdate = 2012-03-20 | url = http://www.cubanet.org/CNews/y99/oct99/25o12.htm | archivedate = 2012-03-20 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，降雨还导致烟田被淹<ref name="cnn" />。整个古巴共有2万7336套房屋因洪灾受损，730套彻底被毁<ref name="cubstuff" />，还有13家[[医院|医院]]受到一定程度的影响。哈瓦那有154个街区因风暴停电<ref name="cubreport" />。艾琳一共夺走了该国4人的生命<ref name = "bbc" />，其中两人是在哈瓦那因触电身亡<ref name="cubreport"/>。

=== 佛罗里达州 ===
[[Image:Hurricane_Irene_-_Flooding.jpg|right]]
途经[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]期间，艾琳给[[威卡礁|威卡礁]]（{{lang|en|Key Vaca}}）带去了0.7米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="glos" />。|group="注"}}，基韦斯特岛也有0.5米高。飓风产生的持续风速最高达到每小时127公里，阵风时速最快的则是[[大松礁岛|大松礁岛]]（{{lang|en|Big Pine Key}}）记录下的164公里<ref name="tcr" />。佛罗里达礁岛群普降暴雨，基韦斯特的降雨量达305毫米。整个群岛到处都有公路被洪水淹没，政府为此封闭了[[美国国道1|美国国道1]]的80公里路段。风暴还在[[伊斯拉摩拉_(佛罗里达州)|伊斯拉摩拉]]催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，导致3段房屋受到严重破坏。中等强度阵风造成整个礁岛群停电，但总体破坏较为轻微<ref name="cnnkey">{{cite news | author = John Zarrella & Jeff Flock | year = 1999 | title = Hurricane Irene pulls plug on 700,000 utility customers | publisher = Cnn.com | accessdate = 2006-06-28 | url = http://www.cnn.com/US/9910/15/irene.07/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061224164936/http://www.cnn.com/US/9910/15/irene.07/ | archivedate = 2006-12-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

气旋经过佛罗里达州期间仍有飓风强度，但该州本土没有报道出现飓风强度狂风。正式纪录中的最高风速是[[迈阿密海滩|迈阿密海滩]]的每小时97公里，而准确的最强阵风时速则是[[维罗海滩_(佛罗里达州)|维罗海滩]]记录下的114公里。此外根据[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]的报告，南佛罗里达水域管理局在[[贝尔格莱德_(佛罗里达州)|贝尔格莱德]][[奥基乔比湖|奥基乔比湖]]附近记录下了每小时150公里的阵风，不过这很可能是由小型[[中尺度气象学|中尺度气旋]]诱发的[[下击暴流|下击暴流]]导致<ref name="tcr" />。佛罗里达州东南部普降暴雨，降雨量最高的是[[博因顿海滩_(佛罗里达州)|博因顿海滩]]，有443毫米，[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密大都会区]]也有多处降水达到255到380毫米。[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]]和[[棕榈滩县|棕榈滩县]]有4场龙卷风着陆，其中一场的[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]为{{lang|en|F1}}，另外三场为{{lang|en|F0}}，一共导致3人受伤<ref name="mnws">{{cite web | author = Miami National Weather Service | year = 1999 | title = Summary of Hurricane Irene in Southeast Florida | accessdate = 2014-07-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131227154709/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/mfl/?n=1999_irene | deadurl = no | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/mfl/?n=1999_irene | archivedate = 2013-12-27 }}</ref>。
[[File:Hurricane_Irene_-_Cows.jpg|left]]

强烈的阵风导致[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]到[[西棕榈滩|西棕榈滩]]之间地区有70万人失去电力供应，美国国家飓风中心也在其中。中心停电的时间虽短，但却延误了一个半小时来重新启动计算机，这些计算机中保留有来自[[美国中西部|美国中西部]]和[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]的信息。阵风太强还导致[[佛罗里达电力和照明|佛罗里达电力和照明公司]]官员无法修复输电线缆，并且艾琳产生的洪水还淹没了地下线路，令维修工作只有到洪水退去后才能开始<ref name="cnnkey" />。有5人因走到了断裂电线停落的水上导致触电身亡，其中3人还是一家人<ref name="bbcfla">{{cite news | author = BBC News | title = Hurricane Irene heads north | accessdate = 2014-07-27 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/477045.stm | date = 1999-10-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224130031/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/477045.stm | archivedate = 2013-12-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。飓风产生的暴雨导致多条道路和河流被淹，许多汽车受困<ref name="cnnkey" />。有三人因将车开进了河中而溺毙<ref name="tcr" />。部分区域的洪水持续了近一周之久，数以百计的居民无家可归，上千人失去了同外界的联系。佛罗里达州东南部一共遭受了2.62亿美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|262000000|1999}}}}美元）的财产损失<ref name="fldam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for Florida (1) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172233/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358696 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358696 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | date =  }}</ref>。

艾琳还对佛罗里达州东南部造成了严重的农业损失，总额达到3.38亿美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|338000000|1999}}}}美元）<ref name="fldam" />。一个农场有30头牛因洪水死亡，不过农场主通过把觅食区转移到地势更高的地方而保住了另外1700头牛<ref name="femacow">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 1999 | title = FEMA Photo Library | accessdate = 2009-01-06 | archivedate = 2009-01-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090106163359/http://www.photolibrary.fema.gov/photolibrary/photo_details.do?id=314 | url = http://www.photolibrary.fema.gov/photolibrary/photo_details.do?id=314 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。根据初步估算数字，洪水摧毁了沿途5%到15%的果林<ref name="floridajuice">{{cite web | author = Florida Department of Citrus | year = 1999 | title = Florida Citrus Outlook 1999–2000 season | accessdate = 2009-03-26 | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326065201/http://www.floridajuice.com/user_upload/files/outlok99_422f263b25b01.pdf | url = http://www.floridajuice.com/user_upload/files/outlok99_422f263b25b01.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。洪灾延迟了[[玉米|玉米]]和[[菜椒|菜椒]]的冬季播种，还破坏了[[西红柿|西红柿]]植株，迫使[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]种植户补种受损的作物<ref name="nass">{{cite report | author = National Agricultural Statistics Service | year = 2000 | title = 1999 Vegetables Summary}}</ref>。飓风破坏了甘蔗、蔬菜和柑橘类作物<ref name="usda">{{cite report | author = National Agricultural Statistics Service | year = 1999 | title = Weekly Weather and Crop Bulletin}}</ref>，风暴过后还出现了[[柑桔溃疡病|柑桔溃疡病]]蔓延。由于农作物损失惨重，[[美国农业部|美国农业部]]宣布[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]]、[[柯里尔县|柯里尔县]]、迈阿密-戴德县和门罗县为灾区，受灾农民可以申请低息应急贷款<ref name="agrideclar">{{cite web | author = US Department of Agriculture | year = 2000 | title = GLICKMAN MAKES DISASTER DECLARATION FOR FOUR FLORIDA COUNTIES | accessdate = 2006-07-05 | url = http://www.fsa.usda.gov/pas/newsroom/releases/2000/03/0093.htm | archivedate = 2005-09-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050909050915/http://www.fsa.usda.gov/pas/newsroom/releases/2000/03/0093.htm }}</ref>。
[[Image:Irene_beach_erosion.jpg|right]]]]

佛罗里达州东部海岸线之前曾因飓风丹尼斯和飓风弗洛伊德出现中等程度的[[海岸侵蚀|海滩侵蚀]]，这次艾琳的到来更是雪上加霜。部分民房的地基因[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]而暴露出来，其中一些已无法居住<ref name="srh" />。海滩侵蚀的损失共计达到2100万美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|21000000|1999}}}}美元）<ref name="menws">{{cite web | author = Melbourne National Weather Service | year = 1999 | title = Hurricane Irene Preliminary Summary 10-16-99 | accessdate = 2008-10-16 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/mlb/irenesum.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081016115202/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/mlb/irenesum.html | archivedate = 2008-10-16 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。许多海滩此后直到有更多沙子补充或是梯道重建后才再度开放。强烈的海浪和北风导致[[印第安河泻湖|印第安河泻湖]]的许多船坞受损或被毁<ref name="srh" />。[[马丁县_(佛罗里达州)|马丁县]]和[[圣卢西亚县_(佛罗里达州)|圣卢西亚县]]的降雨量在127到229毫米之间，致使260套民宅被淹。马丁县、圣卢西亚县和[[布里瓦德县_(佛罗里达州)|布里瓦德县]]共有1114套房屋因时速97到113公里的阵风受到轻度损伤，还有34套严重受损。此外，狂风还推毁了一套移动房屋，另有465套受损，其中15套程度严重。有555幢商业建筑受到轻度破坏，阵风还刮倒了约1000棵树。[[佛罗里达州528号公路|佛罗里达州528号公路]]的一座桥梁上有一艘大型驳船因海况恶劣而从系泊处扯下<ref name="menws" />。[[弗莱格勒县|弗莱格勒县]]有4户民房严重受损，另有173套房屋和18家商户受到轻度破坏<ref name="fldam3">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114034910/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358709 | deadurl = yes | title = Event Report for Florida (2) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358709 }}</ref>。佛罗里达州东北部一共遭受了约5100万美元（1999年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|51000000|1999}}}}美元）的破坏<ref name="fldam2">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172123/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358708 | title = Event Report for Florida (2) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~358708 }}</ref>。

=== 巴哈马 ===
飓风艾琳从[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]西北部附近洋面经过，当地出现了中等程度洪灾<ref name="bahis">{{cite web | author = Bahamas Department of Meteorology | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Cyclones which affected the Bahamas | accessdate = 2006-06-28 | archivedate = 2007-09-29 | deadurl = yes | url = http://bahamasweather.org.bs/tropical/history/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070929025909/http://bahamasweather.org.bs/tropical/history/ }}</ref>，还受到了几场龙卷风的袭击。其中一场龙卷风造成[[阿巴科群岛|阿巴科岛]]一人丧生，还对[[马什港|马什港]]（{{lang|en|Marsh Harbour}}）构成破坏<ref name="bahdam">{{cite web | author = Abaco Journal on the World Wide Web | year = 1999 | title = The Year in Review | accessdate = 2012-02-04 | url = http://oii.net/Journal/jan00/year.shtml | archivedate = 2012-02-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204215503/http://oii.net/Journal/jan00/year.shtml }}</ref>。一辆卡车在倾盆大雨中因码头湿滑开入水中，导致4人间接因风暴遇难<ref name="cnnkey" />。

=== 南、北卡罗莱纳州和中大西洋各州 ===
[[Image:Irene_1999_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
南卡罗莱纳州东部的降雨量在125到150毫米之间。洪水导致多条道路封闭，[[乔治敦县_(南卡罗莱纳州)|乔治敦县]]还有一些公路被冲毁<ref name="scdam">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for South Carolina (1) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114034953/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~377746 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~377746 }}</ref>。[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]出现时速77公里的中等强度阵风，刮倒了一些树木，还令多条供电线路中断，造成零星停电。沿海因大风出现轻度海滩侵蚀<ref name="scdam2">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for South Carolina (2) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114034839/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~377748 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~377748 }}</ref>。

沿北卡罗莱纳州海岸平行移动期间，艾琳令该州普降暴雨，局部降雨量最高达到280毫米，另有多处记录下超过152毫米降水<ref name="tcr" />。暴雨导致北卡罗莱纳州多条河流严重泛滥，其中许多地区在不到一个月前由飓风弗洛伊德引发的洪水尚未退去。由于[[地表径流|径流]]的影响，[[塔河|塔河]]、[[开普菲尔河|开普菲尔河]]和[[纽斯河|纽斯河]]全部决口。洪灾还造成[[霍克县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|霍克县]]中南部的一个水坝溢出<ref name="newsreports">{{cite web | author = Various | year = 1999 | title = News Reports from Irene | accessdate = 2014-07-27 | url = http://www.greatdreams.com/irene99.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140114031102/http://www.greatdreams.com/irene99.htm | archivedate = 2014-01-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

艾琳在该州催出生两场龙卷风，其中一场{{lang|en|F0}}级出现在[[昂斯洛县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|昂斯洛县]]<ref name="nctorn">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for North Carolina (1) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372402 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172138/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372402 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，另一场出现在[[帕斯阔坦克县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|帕斯阔坦克县]]，为{{lang|en|F2}}级，这场{{lang|en|F2}}级龙卷风摧毁了两辆拖车，令多套房屋受损，导致1人受伤<ref name="nctorn2">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for North Carolina (2) | accessdate = 2006-07-06 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372431 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172215/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372431 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。严重的洪水迫使整个北卡罗莱纳州大量道路封闭，还引发了多起交通事故<ref name="ncdam2">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for North Carolina (3) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372403 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172203/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372403 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。一名男子在因[[滑水_(轮胎)|道路湿滑]]引发的交通事故中丧生，属于飓风艾琳间接导致的人员伤亡。虽然引发了严重的洪灾，但风暴总体上对北卡罗莱纳州造成的破坏很小<ref name="ncdam3">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 1999 | title = Event Report for North Carolina (4) | accessdate = 2006-11-14 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372396 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061114172331/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~372396 | archivedate = 2006-11-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

艾琳还给[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]东南部带去暴雨，降雨量最高的[[切萨皮克_(弗吉尼亚州)|切萨皮克]]达到305毫米<ref name="tcr" />。这些降水引发了大规模的街道水淹，部分地区报告的积水达到1.2米深<ref name="vadam">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110525030126/http://members.cox.net/wxr/irene99.htm | author = Portsmouth Weather Records Service | year = 1999 | title = Hurricane Irene Summary | accessdate = 2011-05-25 | archivedate = 2011-05-25 | url = http://members.cox.net/wxr/irene99.htm | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

== 善后 ==
飓风过去后，[[国际红十字与红新月运动|国际红十字与红新月运动]]为古巴发出紧急呼吁。这次呼吁共计筹得21万7498[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]，为生活在临时避难所的1.2万人提供卫生用品、家居用品、净水药片和水容器。呼吁中还请求[[国际社会|国际社会]]提供维修物资，改善该国面对未来灾难时的应对能力。古巴红十字会调集了4500名志愿者赶赴灾区，向伤者提供紧急救援，分发餐点和医疗用品，并与血站合作<ref name="cubstuff" />。由政府控制的各个新闻媒体在报道中保证会提供维修用品，但许多人在风暴过去数周后仍然只能生活在受损的房屋中<ref name="morecub">{{cite web | author = José Orlando González Bridón | year = 1999 | title = UNFULFILLED PROMISES TO VICTIMS OF HURRICANE IRENE | publisher = CUBA FREE PRESS | accessdate = 2014-07-27 | url = http://www.cubafreepress.org/art2/cubap991201j.html | archivedate = 2012-02-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204172425/http://www.cubafreepress.org/art2/cubap991201j.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

飓风离开佛罗里达州数天后，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]宣布[[佛罗里达州行政区划|该州18个县]]为灾区，让受到影响的企业和业主可以申请联邦援助，例如用于临时住房、小范围房屋维修或其他与灾害相关费用的资金补贴。此外，克林顿还为佛罗里达州发布了紧急声明，提供联邦资源协助垃圾清理和紧急服务工作<ref name="declar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 1999 | title = Disaster Aid Ordered For Florida Hurricane Recovery | accessdate = 2012-02-05 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=8619 | archivedate = 2012-02-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020707/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=8619 }}</ref>。总统还宣布，北卡罗莱纳州之前因飓风弗洛伊德而获联邦援助的66个县还可以因飓风艾琳而继续获得更多的援助<ref name="ncdecl">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 1999 | title = Hurricane Irene Victims Now Eligible For Federal Aid | accessdate = 2006-07-06 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9194 | archivedate = 2012-02-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020712/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=9194 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

巴哈马有许多志愿者协助清理工作，[[巴哈马皇家国防军|巴哈马皇家国防军]]向灾民发放救灾物资<ref name="bahdam" />。

